node.text:
Power Breakfast Bagel 👊🏼🥯 Japanese souffle omelette, honey ham, baby spinach, @bakerandcooksg beetroot relish and 7-grain bagel || initial idea was to have a sweet Tamagoyaki but the souffle version turned out to be a more practical and feasible option with the available kitchen tools. Indeed a pretty massive portion but the components pulled together surprisingly well 😋
